                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="3ra" to="217vb"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2375Synaxa#FirstHalf">Sǝnkǝssār (General record): First half of the year</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     <note>Salām-hymns appear only from the month <foreign xml:lang="gez">Tāḫśāś</foreign> <locus target="#102va"/>. Initially, they appear following a commemorative note <locus from="102va" to="106va"/>.
                        Subsequently, they are grouped at the end of each day. </note>
                 
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                        <locus from="3ra" to="34va"/>
                        <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2375Synaxa#Maskaram">Sǝnkǝssār (General record): Commemorative notices for the month of Maskaram</title>
