                        <item xml:id="e7">
                           <desc>Originally, blank spaces for the names of all supplicants were filled in by <ref target="#h1">Hand 1</ref> up untill <locus target="#42"/>. Subsequently, they were filled in unsystematically by <ref target="#h1">Hand 1</ref>, 
                              some were left blank, while others were filled in by <ref target="#h3">Hand 3</ref>. In many instances, the original names have been washed out from the supplication formulas, leaving them blank or newly filled with different names.</desc>
                        </item>
                           <item xml:id="e8">
                           <locus target="#1r #2r #218r #218v #219r"/>
                           <desc>Pen trials, notes.</desc>
                        </item>
                     
